  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1931",
  "title": "StarRating does not indicates non relevant refinements",
  "body": "When using `<Configure filters=\"rating>2\"/>` along with StarRating widget, ratings 1 and 2 should be disabled but they are not.\r\n\r\nIt seems to be triggered because we are not using the stats while constructing the StarRating widget.\r\n\r\nEither we should implement it with ConnectMultiRange or we should forward stats from connectRange.\r\n\r\nCc @mthuret ",
